{"tid":1391132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"80%南韓人表示：不再支持C.朗拿度","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T02:05:51.000Z","uid":173952,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5f52b0048034b4619254765954aa5425428d8a64","tid":1391132,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"據韓媒《MBC Sports》調查，八成南韓人表示，不會再支持C.朗拿度（C.Ronaldo）。<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度在訪韓友誼賽中未登場，引起南韓國民不滿。7月30日，南韓19歲以上的501名民眾接受了調查，79.4%的人選擇了「以後不再為C.朗拿度加油」，「今後還會繼續為C.朗拿度助威」的僅佔9.3%。<br />\n<br />\n  參加調查的球迷中45.9%（約230人）曾是C.朗拿度的球迷，其中85.6%表示不再支持C.朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n  針對該事件責任方在誰，25.3%球迷選擇了南韓職業足球聯盟，22.7%球迷選C.朗拿度，18.3%球迷選祖記，17.3%球迷選主辦方。<br />\n<br />\n少左400個fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6963fbda09dffdce23c9086911f7d26983bc18eb","tid":1391132,"uid":134997,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:39:29.000Z","msg":"C朗咁黑人憎 好合理"},{"pid":"e147a2930c81c6070ab22d8f750afd49605abb4d","tid":1391132,"uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"香港訪問某501人，80%支持香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b736eb36b689984090ae8b71c55c9492a699a246","tid":1391132,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗真係唔知幫邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1e45afecb588942558ac7b1a08179295886e55","tid":1391132,"uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"屌你南韓02黑走意大利<br />\n意大利果陣可以衝冠軍"},{"pid":"27a3d269d4f1389c2297a91f3d262301b0bd2f8c","tid":1391132,"uid":210682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"C朗乞人憎係事實"},{"pid":"4da8a41bccf8bc9646e7384428fe2239e6680cb7","tid":1391132,"uid":253826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"